wvstreams (4.0.2-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * New upstream version.  (Closes: Bug#276571)
    - Fixes OpenSSL FTBFS.  (Closes: Bug#281772)
  * Depend on a newer version of BDB.  (Closes: Bug#248522)
  * We now depend on XPLC 0.3.10.
  * Moved /etc/uniconf.conf to libuniconf4.0.
  * Added /etc/default/uniconfd to uniconfd's init script.

